---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pricing | AI Automation & Local SEO | Brew City Automation"
  description="Starting monthly investments for Brew City Automation: automation consulting pilots, AI operations retainers, and multi-location programs—scoped after discovery."
  keywords="AI automation pricing, small business consulting rates, local SEO pricing Milwaukee"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-14 md:px-6 md:py-20">
    <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-badger/45">Pricing</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-ink md:text-5xl">Starting investment</h1>
    <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-badger/80">
      Every business has a different stack and risk tolerance. These are <strong class="text-ink">starting at</strong>{' '}
      monthly ranges—final scope is confirmed after a working session.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-6">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-badger/10 bg-paper p-8 shadow-card">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Automation Pilot</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-badger/50">
          Starting at <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink">$1,100</span>/mo
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-badger/80">
          Workflow discovery, one primary automation or AI surface, documentation, and a 30-day stabilization window.
          Ideal for teams ready to ship a narrow pilot with clear KPIs.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-badger/10 bg-paper p-8 shadow-card">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">AI &amp; Local Growth Retainer</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-badger/50">
          Starting at <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink">$1,850</span>/mo
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-badger/80">
          Ongoing automation iteration plus local SEO depth: Google Business Profile, review workflows, localized
          content cadence, and optional chat or voice—coordinated as one system.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-badger/10 bg-paper p-8 shadow-card">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Multi-location / Brand governance</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-badger/50">
          Starting at <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink">$2,600</span>/mo
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-badger/80">
          Coordinated listings, automation standards, and reporting across multiple territories or brands—custom SOW
          after audit.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 text-sm text-badger/65">
      Paid media and full web builds are quoted separately when needed. Wisconsin sales tax may apply. Month-to-month
      on standard agreements unless you prefer an annual commitment for a reduced rate.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 rounded-2xl bg-ink px-6 py-8 text-paper">
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Pick the right first step</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-paper/65">
        We will map quick wins vs. compounding bets—automation first, marketing second, or both in parallel if your
        team can absorb the change.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact/"
        class="mt-6 inline-flex rounded-full bg-paper px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink hover:bg-paper-dim"
      >
        Book a call
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
